      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Heraldry Scholar Bailey${action:Talk}<BR>Kamu bisa mendapatkan Mutated Chubaka Jewel di <FONT color=#a82424>Road of No Return</FONT>, Mutated Scarlet Scythe Jewel di <FONT color=#a82424>Death Basin</FONT>, Mutated Dark Scream Jewel di <FONT color=#a82424>Sanctuary Core</FONT>, dan Mutated Keruru Jewel di <FONT color=#a82424>Prayer's Refugee</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
